{"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handleopenurl:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"handleOpenURL:","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)handleOpenURL:","symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"handleOpenURL:"}],"title":"handleOpenURL:","role":"symbol"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","text":"BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"handleOpenURL:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"NSURL","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSURL","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"url","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"url","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The URL to process."}]}]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"YES if the URL was handled by Pushwoosh, NO otherwise.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Handles special Pushwoosh URLs, primarily used for:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Test device registration"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Register device for push testing via QR code","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Deep link tracking"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Process tracked deep links from push notifications"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Should be called from your app’s URL handling methods. Returns YES if the URL","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"was a Pushwoosh URL and was handled, NO if it should be processed by your app.","type":"text"}]},{"anchor":"Example","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Example"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Handle URLs in SceneDelegate (iOS 13+):","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["class SceneDelegate: UIResponder, UIWindowSceneDelegate {","","    func scene(_ scene: UIScene, openURLContexts URLContexts: Set<UIOpenURLContext>) {","        guard let url = URLContexts.first?.url else { return }","","        \/\/ First, check if Pushwoosh handles this URL","        if Pushwoosh.configure.handleOpenURL(url) {","            Logger.info(\"URL handled by Pushwoosh\")","            return","        }","","        \/\/ Handle other deep links","        DeepLinkRouter.shared.handle(url)","    }","","    func scene(_ scene: UIScene, continue userActivity: NSUserActivity) {","        guard userActivity.activityType == NSUserActivityTypeBrowsingWeb,","              let url = userActivity.webpageURL else { return }","","        if Pushwoosh.configure.handleOpenURL(url) {","            return","        }","","        UniversalLinkRouter.shared.handle(url)","    }","}","","\/\/ Legacy AppDelegate support","class AppDelegate: UIApplicationDelegate {","","    func application(_ app: UIApplication,","                    open url: URL,","                    options: [UIApplication.OpenURLOptionsKey: Any] = [:]) -> Bool {","","        if Pushwoosh.configure.handleOpenURL(url) {","            return true","        }","","        return DeepLinkRouter.shared.handle(url)","    }","}"]}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Processes deep link URLs for Pushwoosh SDK functionality.","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/handleOpenURL:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","role":"collection","title":"PushwooshCore"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/handleOpenURL:":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"handleOpenURL:"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handleopenurl:","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Processes deep link URLs for Pushwoosh SDK functionality."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/handleOpenURL:","title":"handleOpenURL:","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"handleOpenURL:","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[],"title":"PWConfiguration","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration"}}}